1134
01:18:49,897 --> 01:18:51,648
But honestly,

1135
01:18:51,732 --> 01:18:55,194
I'm happy that you know who you are.

1136
01:18:57,988 --> 01:18:59,489
You're brave.

1137
01:18:59,948 --> 01:19:01,533
Not like me.

1138
01:19:46,662 --> 01:19:47,746
Get lost.

1139
01:19:48,413 --> 01:19:49,498
You hiding?

1140
