1203
01:23:52,574 --> 01:23:54,034
My buttons are off.

1204
01:23:54,535 --> 01:23:56,328
That weren't no DJ

1205
01:23:56,411 --> 01:23:59,414
That was hazy cosmic jive

1206
01:24:01,917 --> 01:24:04,044
What do you want for dinner?

1207
