"Meet" is one finger, not two.
See? This is, like, the legs.

1244
01:28:28,559 --> 01:28:29,643
No!

1245
01:28:29,726 --> 01:28:30,978
No, no, no! I mean...

1246
01:28:31,061 --> 01:28:32,396
Oh my God!

1247
01:28:32,479 --> 01:28:33,981
It's fine. I get it.

1248
01:28:35,023 --> 01:28:36,942
